681
00:30:47,900 --> 00:30:49,400
[SPEAKER_01] A sama činjenica da je to sa prebašeno

682
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:50,680
[SPEAKER_01] na jedan viši sud

683
00:30:50,680 --> 00:30:53,900
[SPEAKER_01] sigurno ne ide u prilog našim građanima

684
00:30:53,900 --> 00:30:55,480
[SPEAKER_01] koji su gore.

685
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto mislite da se čekali tri tijena

686
00:30:58,039 --> 00:30:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] da se razglasi o toj tijena?

687
00:30:59,559 --> 00:31:02,220
[SPEAKER_01] Pa zašto? Zato što to dolazi iz jedne kuhinje

688
00:31:02,220 --> 00:31:04,180
[SPEAKER_01] jer nije to sasvim slučajno

689
00:31:04,180 --> 00:31:06,319
[SPEAKER_01] da je tamo nekakvi zastupnici možemo,

690
00:31:06,319 --> 00:31:08,500
[SPEAKER_01] da su tamo nekakvi bliski suradnici

691
00:31:08,500 --> 00:31:10,039
[SPEAKER_01] aktualnog radonačelnika.

692
00:31:10,039 --> 00:31:13,359
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedna svita ljudi

693
00:31:13,359 --> 00:31:15,420
[SPEAKER_01] koja je u najmanju ruku

694
00:31:15,420 --> 00:31:17,160
[SPEAKER_01] sve samo neobiteljska.

695
00:31:17,900 --> 00:31:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] i koja zagovara apsolutno kontra teme.

696
00:31:20,460 --> 00:31:22,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znači nije njima obitelj na prvom mjestu

697
00:31:22,539 --> 00:31:23,980
[SPEAKER_01] i nisu njima ta djeca na prvom mjestu.

698
00:31:23,980 --> 00:31:25,740
[SPEAKER_01] Možda ja sad grešim,

699
00:31:25,740 --> 00:31:28,160
[SPEAKER_01] ali to je moj osobni stavio, moje viđenje

700
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:30,400
[SPEAKER_01] i to je trebalo staviti sve pod tepih.

701
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:32,220
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, eto je ugledalo to svjetlo dana,

702
00:31:32,220 --> 00:31:33,839
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda vidite da kako HDZ

703
00:31:33,839 --> 00:31:35,319
[SPEAKER_01] zdušno pokušava obraniti

704
00:31:35,319 --> 00:31:37,859
[SPEAKER_01] te teme vezane za možemo,

705
00:31:37,859 --> 00:31:40,059
[SPEAKER_01] jer očito su i oni infiltrirani u tu cijelu priču,

706
00:31:40,059 --> 00:31:42,220
[SPEAKER_01] ali i možda zbog

707
00:31:42,220 --> 00:31:44,759
[SPEAKER_01] ne pokovariti nekakvu buduću koaliciju

708
00:31:44,759 --> 00:31:46,440
[SPEAKER_01] na pomolu između HDZ-a i možemo.

709
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:49,180
[SPEAKER_01] Što po meni je vrlo, vrlo izgledno.

710
00:31:49,180 --> 00:31:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] Zamušena neka priča.

711
00:31:50,539 --> 00:31:51,319
[SPEAKER_01] Jako.

712
00:31:51,319 --> 00:31:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bih se svejedno vratio malo na udrugu,

713
00:31:53,920 --> 00:31:56,240
[SPEAKER_00] jer ipak je to ključna stvar oko koje smo tu

714
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:58,799
[SPEAKER_00] i sviđa mi se, rekao, kontaktirao sam vas

715
00:31:58,799 --> 00:32:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] kada sam vidio da radite jednu,

716
00:32:00,059 --> 00:32:01,900
[SPEAKER_00] rekao bih, ozbiljniju stvar,

717
00:32:01,900 --> 00:32:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] da ste se pokrenuli, to zbilja ozbiljno izgleda.

718
00:32:05,119 --> 00:32:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] Zanima me baš pitanje vezano uz političke opcije.

719
00:32:08,539 --> 00:32:10,480
[SPEAKER_00] Planirate li možda u budućnosti

720
00:32:10,480 --> 00:32:12,839
[SPEAKER_00] iznjadriti neke ljude koji će možda

721
00:32:12,839 --> 00:32:14,839
[SPEAKER_00] postati dionici nekih politika,

722
00:32:14,839 --> 00:32:16,640
[SPEAKER_00] koji su baš ono uže krug unutar

723
00:32:16,640 --> 00:32:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatskog bila,

724
00:32:17,420 --> 00:32:19,299
[SPEAKER_00] ili planirate li vi možda kao takvi

725
00:32:19,299 --> 00:32:20,859
[SPEAKER_00] podržati neku političku opciju?

726
00:32:20,859 --> 00:32:23,720
[SPEAKER_01] Eta, to je dobro pitanje.

727
00:32:23,720 --> 00:32:25,240
[SPEAKER_01] I tu je odgovor,

728
00:32:25,240 --> 00:32:27,960
[SPEAKER_01] odgovor je negdje između ova vaša dva pitanja.

729
00:32:28,759 --> 00:32:31,619
[SPEAKER_01] Mi ćemo biti otvoreni za jednu i drugu opciju.

730
00:32:31,619 --> 00:32:33,160
[SPEAKER_01] Da li ćemo mi sad kroz naš rad

731
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:34,440
[SPEAKER_01] iznjadriti, ne znam,

732
00:32:34,440 --> 00:32:36,500
[SPEAKER_01] takve ljude koji bi možda mogli biti

733
00:32:36,500 --> 00:32:38,940
[SPEAKER_01] nosioci nekakvih politika u Hrvatskogu?

734
00:32:38,940 --> 00:32:39,839
[SPEAKER_01] Možda, možda.

735
00:32:39,839 --> 00:32:41,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mogu reći sa sigurnoviću,

736
00:32:41,039 --> 00:32:42,400
[SPEAKER_01] bilo bi vrlo neodgovorno od mene.

737
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:44,220
[SPEAKER_01] Da li ćemo mi podržati nekoga

738
00:32:44,220 --> 00:32:45,640
[SPEAKER_01] na nekakvim idućim parlamentima?

739
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:46,779
[SPEAKER_01] To svakako.

740
00:32:46,779 --> 00:32:48,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ali koga ćemo podržati?

741
00:32:48,220 --> 00:32:49,380
[SPEAKER_01] Podržati ćemo onoga ko će

742
00:32:49,380 --> 00:32:52,279
[SPEAKER_01] pokušati proklamirati i zastupati

743
00:32:52,279 --> 00:32:54,940
[SPEAKER_01] rješenja koja ćemo mi nuditi.

744
00:32:55,779 --> 00:32:57,660
[SPEAKER_01] Ali rješenja koja neće biti

745
00:32:57,660 --> 00:32:59,220
[SPEAKER_01] ni malo politički ostrašćena.

746
00:32:59,220 --> 00:33:00,859
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, općenita ostrašćenost,

747
00:33:00,859 --> 00:33:02,160
[SPEAKER_01] meni, ja to ne volim.

748
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:04,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ajmo biti pragmatični,

749
00:33:04,079 --> 00:33:05,039
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo biti racionalni,

750
00:33:05,039 --> 00:33:06,039
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo probati stvarno,

751
00:33:06,039 --> 00:33:08,500
[SPEAKER_01] a pritom pričamo isključivo

752
00:33:08,500 --> 00:33:09,920
[SPEAKER_01] o ovim nacionalnim pitanjima.

753
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi je onaj ko počne nuditi,

754
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:14,180
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno ko počne zastupati

755
00:33:14,180 --> 00:33:16,460
[SPEAKER_01] dobre stvari koje će se promijeniti

756
00:33:16,460 --> 00:33:17,900
[SPEAKER_01] od ove demografije,

757
00:33:17,900 --> 00:33:19,559
[SPEAKER_01] od gospodarstva, od zdravstva.

758
00:33:19,559 --> 00:33:20,579
[SPEAKER_01] A mi se možemo nabrati,

759
00:33:20,579 --> 00:33:22,500
[SPEAKER_01] imamo probleme na malte ne na svim poljima.

760
00:33:23,259 --> 00:33:25,380
[SPEAKER_01] Našu podrušku će imati.

761
00:33:25,380 --> 00:33:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto prema vama to nije se moglo raditi

762
00:33:27,220 --> 00:33:28,519
[SPEAKER_00] u sklopu domovinskog pokreta?

763
00:33:28,519 --> 00:33:30,660
[SPEAKER_00] Što se dovodilo, kako je to zaiskrilo?

764
00:33:30,660 --> 00:33:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ipak ste vi stvarali tu organizaciju,

765
00:33:33,019 --> 00:33:34,319
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, poznati ste po terenu,

766
00:33:34,319 --> 00:33:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] poznati ste po ljudima,

767
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] da ste vi upravo stvarali tu organizaciju,

768
00:33:38,000 --> 00:33:40,140
[SPEAKER_00] barem što se tiče tog rada na terenu.

769
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:44,240
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto takav isti stav koji imate sada

770
00:33:44,240 --> 00:33:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] nije predvladao, recimo, u domovinskom pokretu?

771
00:33:46,579 --> 00:33:48,339
[SPEAKER_01] To je dobro pitanje.

772
00:33:48,339 --> 00:33:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] Na to pitanje moram priznat da ja osobno

773
00:33:50,119 --> 00:33:51,339
[SPEAKER_01] nisam još odgonetnuo,

774
00:33:51,339 --> 00:33:53,980
[SPEAKER_01] dao sam sebi pravi odgovor.

775
00:33:53,980 --> 00:33:56,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ali vidite, u domovinski pokret,

776
00:33:56,380 --> 00:33:57,680
[SPEAKER_01] ja nikad u nijednoj političkoj stranici

777
00:33:57,680 --> 00:33:58,900
[SPEAKER_01] prije domovinskog pokreta nisam bilo.

778
00:33:58,900 --> 00:34:00,900
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nemam iskaznicu ni SDP-a, ni HDZ-a.

779
00:34:00,900 --> 00:34:03,079
[SPEAKER_01] Jedina i prva politička opcija koja sam imao

780
00:34:03,079 --> 00:34:04,180
[SPEAKER_01] bio, to je bio domovinski pokret,

781
00:34:04,180 --> 00:34:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji sam stvarno svesredno skoro tri godine,

782
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:09,179
[SPEAKER_01] ono, doslovce, po 18 sati dnevno radio

783
00:34:09,179 --> 00:34:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] i stvarao sam ga.

784
00:34:10,000 --> 00:34:11,739
[SPEAKER_01] Jer sam vjerovao u ideju.

785
00:34:11,739 --> 00:34:14,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ideja je bila, po meni, onako,

786
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:15,699
[SPEAKER_01] bogom dana.

787
00:34:15,699 --> 00:34:17,480
[SPEAKER_01] Bogom dana ideja, nešto, ono svjetlo

788
00:34:17,480 --> 00:34:18,880
[SPEAKER_01] na kraju tunela kad ga ugledate.

789
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:20,960
[SPEAKER_01] I stvarno smo se, i ne samo ja,

790
00:34:20,960 --> 00:34:22,840
[SPEAKER_01] nego cijeli moj tim ljudi, cijela ekipa ljudi,

791
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:24,480
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno smo se predali, smo se tome

792
00:34:24,480 --> 00:34:26,059
[SPEAKER_01] i radili smo to zdušno.

793
00:34:26,059 --> 00:34:28,579
[SPEAKER_01] E sad, dogodilo se to što se dogodilo

794
00:34:28,579 --> 00:34:30,380
[SPEAKER_01] sa domovinskim pokretom gdje je abdicira

795
00:34:30,380 --> 00:34:32,619
[SPEAKER_01] u tom trenutku aktualni predsjednik Miroslav Škoro,

796
00:34:32,619 --> 00:34:35,800
[SPEAKER_01] ali pritome, moja ostavka je ostala uvijek,

797
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:37,360
[SPEAKER_01] ne znaš, zašto si podnio ostavku?

798
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:38,300
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto si podnio ostavku?

799
00:34:38,300 --> 00:34:39,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam kao popagaje...

800
00:34:39,619 --> 00:34:40,239
[SPEAKER_01] Hajmo to demistificirati.

801
00:34:40,239 --> 00:34:41,920
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ajmo to demistificirati.

802
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:43,280
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja sam bio glavni tajnik.

803
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:45,519
[SPEAKER_01] Imenovam od strane predsjednika stranke.

804
00:34:45,519 --> 00:34:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam bio izabran na skupštini,

805
00:34:47,460 --> 00:34:49,219
[SPEAKER_01] ja nisam bio izabran nekakvim izborima.

806
00:34:49,219 --> 00:34:51,920
[SPEAKER_01] Minimum političke kulture,

807
00:34:51,920 --> 00:34:54,300
[SPEAKER_01] ja znam da ona nije popularna u Hrvatskoj,

808
00:34:54,300 --> 00:34:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ostavke u Hrvatkoj baš i nisu nešto

809
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:57,460
[SPEAKER_01] što smo naučljivi,

810
00:34:57,460 --> 00:34:58,940
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja sam osjećao jednu

811
00:34:58,940 --> 00:35:00,599
[SPEAKER_01] moralnu odgovornost.

812
00:35:00,599 --> 00:35:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je mene čovjek koji je u tom trenutku

813
00:35:02,539 --> 00:35:03,880
[SPEAKER_01] abdicirao, podnio ostavku,

814
00:35:03,880 --> 00:35:05,780
[SPEAKER_01] postavio za glavnog tajnika,

815
00:35:05,780 --> 00:35:07,300
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno imena ovome glavnim tajnikom,

816
00:35:07,300 --> 00:35:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] najmenje što ja mogu napraviti u tom trenutku

817
00:35:09,460 --> 00:35:10,360
[SPEAKER_01] podnijeti ostavku.

818
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto bi ja opterećivao nekog

819
00:35:12,460 --> 00:35:13,760
[SPEAKER_01] budućeg predsjednika

820
00:35:13,760 --> 00:35:16,579
[SPEAKER_01] sa svojim mandatom koji ja retom,

821
00:35:16,579 --> 00:35:18,300
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam se pravio malo mrta,

822
00:35:18,300 --> 00:35:19,119
[SPEAKER_01] pa ja nema veze,

823
00:35:19,119 --> 00:35:19,699
[SPEAKER_01] otišao je predsjednik,

824
00:35:19,699 --> 00:35:20,539
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam dalje glavni tajnik.

825
00:35:20,539 --> 00:35:22,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ja u životu nisam se rodio

826
00:35:22,500 --> 00:35:24,059
[SPEAKER_01] sa mišom idejom da ću biti glavni tajnik

827
00:35:24,059 --> 00:35:25,119
[SPEAKER_01] bilo koje političke stranke,

828
00:35:25,119 --> 00:35:26,280
[SPEAKER_01] ni ću s tim umrijeti.

829
00:35:26,280 --> 00:35:28,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je bio splet okolnosti

830
00:35:28,079 --> 00:35:29,599
[SPEAKER_01] gdje sam se ja zatekao u tom trenutku

831
00:35:29,599 --> 00:35:30,840
[SPEAKER_01] i neko je prepoznao da bi ja

832
00:35:30,840 --> 00:35:31,920
[SPEAKER_01] trebao biti taj glavni tajnik

833
00:35:31,920 --> 00:35:33,079
[SPEAKER_01] i ja mislim da sam svoju idionicu

834
00:35:33,079 --> 00:35:34,480
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo čestito i pošteno odradio.

835
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:36,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ponosan sam na to.

836
00:35:36,420 --> 00:35:40,659
[SPEAKER_01] Da li sadašnji ovaj DP kao takav...

837
00:35:40,659 --> 00:35:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] Samo da vas pitam,

838
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:43,179
[SPEAKER_00] je li zbog toga što je Miroslav Škoro

839
00:35:43,179 --> 00:35:44,260
[SPEAKER_00] otišao, otišli ste vi?

840
00:35:44,260 --> 00:35:48,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nikad nisam ni došao

841
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] u tu priču zbog Miroslava Škore.

842
00:35:50,460 --> 00:35:52,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam cijenio i poštovao sam

843
00:35:52,119 --> 00:35:53,360
[SPEAKER_01] Miroslav Škoru kao takvoga,

844
00:35:53,360 --> 00:35:54,980
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja sam došao tu zbog ideje.

845
00:35:54,980 --> 00:35:56,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ideja koju je baštinio.

846
00:35:56,719 --> 00:35:59,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ideja na kojoj je nastao domovinski pokret

847
00:35:59,179 --> 00:36:00,139
[SPEAKER_01] i bila ideja koja je

848
00:36:00,139 --> 00:36:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] ja je dan danas zastupan.

849
00:36:01,579 --> 00:36:02,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ja neću odstupiti od te ideje.

850
00:36:02,980 --> 00:36:05,280
[SPEAKER_01] I kroz rad Hrvatskoga bila

851
00:36:05,280 --> 00:36:06,900
[SPEAKER_01] i ne samo ja kad govorim,

852
00:36:06,900 --> 00:36:08,920
[SPEAKER_01] ja onda pričam za cijelu skupinu

853
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:10,139
[SPEAKER_01] ovih ljudi koji su se okupili

854
00:36:10,139 --> 00:36:11,199
[SPEAKER_01] i koji se okupljuju.

855
00:36:11,539 --> 00:36:13,159
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo sad, evo, obišli smo Slavoni,

856
00:36:13,159 --> 00:36:14,119
[SPEAKER_01] obišli smo Dalmaciju.

857
00:36:14,119 --> 00:36:15,719
[SPEAKER_01] Mi ćemo sad u narednim tjednima

858
00:36:15,719 --> 00:36:16,639
[SPEAKER_01] da izaćemo podružnice.

859
00:36:16,639 --> 00:36:17,920
[SPEAKER_01] Znači mi ćemo premrežiti

860
00:36:17,920 --> 00:36:19,699
[SPEAKER_01] cijelu Hrvatsku uzdruž i popreku

861
00:36:19,699 --> 00:36:20,619
[SPEAKER_01] kao što sam je premrežio

862
00:36:20,619 --> 00:36:21,519
[SPEAKER_01] i sa domovinskim pokretom.

863
00:36:21,519 --> 00:36:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ali s kim?

864
00:36:22,119 --> 00:36:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] Sa tim ljudima koji su bili

865
00:36:24,380 --> 00:36:26,179
[SPEAKER_01] vrerni ideji domovinskog pokreta.

866
00:36:26,179 --> 00:36:29,239
[SPEAKER_01] Domovinski pokret je otišao

867
00:36:29,239 --> 00:36:30,519
[SPEAKER_01] u nekom pravcu ili nije,

868
00:36:30,519 --> 00:36:31,400
[SPEAKER_01] možda se ja varam,

869
00:36:31,400 --> 00:36:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali izbori idući će pokazati

870
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:34,260
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je domovinski pokret,

871
00:36:34,260 --> 00:36:36,559
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je ona ideja

872
00:36:36,559 --> 00:36:38,159
[SPEAKER_01] na kojoj smo se mi osnovali

873
00:36:38,159 --> 00:36:39,019
[SPEAKER_01] i na kojoj smo gradili

874
00:36:39,019 --> 00:36:40,519
[SPEAKER_01] cijelu tu politiku

