[SPEAKER_01] mene zanima što

1290
00:45:59,440 --> 00:46:01,480
[SPEAKER_01] prosječan Hrvatskoj misli

1291
00:46:01,480 --> 00:46:02,519
[SPEAKER_01] što je to točno...

1292
00:46:02,519 --> 00:46:04,280
[SPEAKER_01] Ko su te stranke koje pripadaju desnici?

1293
00:46:04,280 --> 00:46:05,739
[SPEAKER_01] Hoćemo pričati o HDZ-u.

1294
00:46:05,739 --> 00:46:07,320
[SPEAKER_01] Demokršćanska stranka,

1295
00:46:07,320 --> 00:46:09,199
[SPEAKER_01] jer oni bi trebali biti...

1296
00:46:09,199 --> 00:46:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, politike koje provode,

1297
00:46:10,860 --> 00:46:13,800
[SPEAKER_01] njihovi svetonazori

1298
00:46:13,800 --> 00:46:14,980
[SPEAKER_01] trenutnog vodstva

1299
00:46:14,980 --> 00:46:16,179
[SPEAKER_01] apsolutno odudaraju

1300
00:46:16,179 --> 00:46:17,340
[SPEAKER_01] ako pričamo o desnici.

1301
00:46:17,340 --> 00:46:18,260
[SPEAKER_01] Hoćemo dalje.

1302
00:46:18,260 --> 00:46:20,159
[SPEAKER_01] Hoćemo pričati, ne znam,

1303
00:46:20,159 --> 00:46:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] o suverenistima.

1304
00:46:21,679 --> 00:46:23,760
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, slušam sad, oni imaju divne inicijative,

1305
00:46:23,760 --> 00:46:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] svašta nešto.

1306
00:46:24,659 --> 00:46:25,500
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, ja imam problem.

1307
00:46:25,500 --> 00:46:26,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mrzim licemjerstvo.

1308
00:46:26,920 --> 00:46:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, da ja dolazim u Sabor,

1309
00:46:29,800 --> 00:46:32,300
[SPEAKER_01] prozivam tamo Plenkovića za XY stvari

1310
00:46:32,300 --> 00:46:33,320
[SPEAKER_01] i podržavam to

1311
00:46:33,320 --> 00:46:34,260
[SPEAKER_01] i trebam ga prozivati,

1312
00:46:34,260 --> 00:46:36,380
[SPEAKER_01] a s druge strane sam sa istim tim Plenkovićem

1313
00:46:36,380 --> 00:46:38,300
[SPEAKER_01] i HDZ-om u nekoliko županija

1314
00:46:38,300 --> 00:46:39,860
[SPEAKER_01] zajedno sa SDSS-om

1315
00:46:39,860 --> 00:46:40,840
[SPEAKER_01] u koaliciji.

1316
00:46:40,840 --> 00:46:42,320
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to nije licemjerno.

1317
00:46:42,320 --> 00:46:43,639
[SPEAKER_01] A onda kad ja njima to kažem,

1318
00:46:43,639 --> 00:46:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] a ne kaže, to je lokalna politika.

1319
00:46:45,079 --> 00:46:45,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ma nemoj.

1320
00:46:46,099 --> 00:46:47,260
[SPEAKER_01] Što znači lokalna politika?

1321
00:46:47,260 --> 00:46:48,579
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, lokalna politika

1322
00:46:48,579 --> 00:46:49,760
[SPEAKER_01] nema veze sa nacionalnom politikom.

1323
00:46:49,760 --> 00:46:50,639
[SPEAKER_01] E, to je krivo.

1324
00:46:50,639 --> 00:46:52,659
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, iz lokalnih politika

1325
00:46:52,659 --> 00:46:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] se treba formirati nacionalna politika

1326
00:46:54,699 --> 00:46:56,119
[SPEAKER_01] svake ozbiljne političke opcije.

1327
00:46:56,119 --> 00:46:57,500
[SPEAKER_01] I zato vam kažem,

1328
00:46:57,500 --> 00:47:00,019
[SPEAKER_01] mi imamo jedan ozbiljan kuršlus

1329
00:47:00,019 --> 00:47:01,340
[SPEAKER_01] na cijeloj političkoj sceni.

1330
00:47:01,340 --> 00:47:03,300
[SPEAKER_01] I ja vam sad opet ponavljam,

1331
00:47:03,300 --> 00:47:05,079
[SPEAKER_01] zamislite da su sutra izbori.

1332
00:47:05,079 --> 00:47:06,599
[SPEAKER_01] Koje su nam desne opcije?

1333
00:47:07,539 --> 00:47:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] A da nema fige u džepu.

1334
00:47:08,539 --> 00:47:09,880
[SPEAKER_01] Nažalost...

1335
00:47:09,880 --> 00:47:11,679
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto se to događa, recimo?

1336
00:47:11,679 --> 00:47:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je jedna konzervativna osoba?

1337
00:47:13,199 --> 00:47:14,719
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto se jedna konzervativna osoba

1338
00:47:14,719 --> 00:47:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] i teško odluči za koga će...

1339
00:47:16,159 --> 00:47:17,519
[SPEAKER_01] A vidite, zašto?

1340
00:47:17,519 --> 00:47:18,980
[SPEAKER_01] Pa zato što je poučena sa svim ovim,

1341
00:47:18,980 --> 00:47:21,940
[SPEAKER_01] ćemo pričati o velikom suverenistu Zvekanoviću

1342
00:47:21,940 --> 00:47:24,980
[SPEAKER_01] koji se prodao za judine škude, što se kaže.

1343
00:47:24,980 --> 00:47:28,119
[SPEAKER_01] A taj čovjek je sinonim nekakvog suverenizma

1344
00:47:28,119 --> 00:47:29,179
[SPEAKER_01] bio sve ove godine.

1345
00:47:29,179 --> 00:47:30,820
[SPEAKER_01] Zastupao takve politike.

1346
00:47:30,820 --> 00:47:31,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam što...

1347
00:47:31,599 --> 00:47:32,980
[SPEAKER_01] O, ti tam puta...

1348
00:47:32,980 --> 00:47:33,639
[SPEAKER_01] On je nestao.

1349
00:47:37,539 --> 00:47:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] I sad zamislite jednog prosječnog građanina

1350
00:47:40,019 --> 00:47:42,300
[SPEAKER_01] koji se tu malo, kao dršno se nešto,

1351
00:47:42,300 --> 00:47:43,360
[SPEAKER_01] sad će ovom politiku pratiti.

1352
00:47:43,360 --> 00:47:45,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kako vam mišljenje traje imati?

1353
00:47:45,179 --> 00:47:47,320
[SPEAKER_01] Da se ovaj prodao za par poduzeća u Šibeniku,

1354
00:47:47,320 --> 00:47:48,579
[SPEAKER_01] javnih poduzeća i ne znam čega.

1355
00:47:48,579 --> 00:47:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo pričati o nedogledu tim preletačima

1356
00:47:52,539 --> 00:47:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] koji su se prodavali na ove i one načine.

1357
00:47:55,260 --> 00:47:58,559
[SPEAKER_01] Tu je kompromitirana cijela politička scena

1358
00:47:58,559 --> 00:48:01,639
[SPEAKER_01] zbog svih tih, kako ih vole zvati, žetončića.

1359
00:48:01,639 --> 00:48:04,400
[SPEAKER_01] Jer mi cijelo vreme imamo trgovačku koaliciju.

1360
00:48:04,400 --> 00:48:06,639
[SPEAKER_01] Pogledajte sad situaciju.

1361
00:48:07,539 --> 00:48:08,699
[SPEAKER_01] Sa HDZ-om na vladu.

1362
00:48:08,699 --> 00:48:09,519
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je li to prirodno?

1363
00:48:09,519 --> 00:48:11,840
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to normalno da su reformisti?

1364
00:48:11,840 --> 00:48:15,619
[SPEAKER_01] Di je dodirna točka reformista i HDZ-a?

1365
00:48:15,619 --> 00:48:17,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ako gledamo onim izvornim strankama

1366
00:48:17,760 --> 00:48:20,440
[SPEAKER_01] i nekakvim postavkama, pa nema veze.

1367
00:48:20,440 --> 00:48:23,340
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, toliko je zagađen taj politički prostor

1368
00:48:23,340 --> 00:48:26,440
[SPEAKER_01] u Hrvatskoj da to više jednostavno ne možete.

1369
00:48:26,440 --> 00:48:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ne možete prosječnom normalnom čovjekom

1370
00:48:28,539 --> 00:48:31,219
[SPEAKER_01] bježi kao od kuge, od svega toga.

1371
00:48:31,219 --> 00:48:32,480
[SPEAKER_01] I tu su problemi.

1372
00:48:32,480 --> 00:48:35,059
[SPEAKER_01] Tu je problem, tek kad počnemo rašišćavati

1373
00:48:35,059 --> 00:48:36,519
[SPEAKER_01] tu cijelu priču.

1374
00:48:36,739 --> 00:48:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja jedinu šansu vidim

1375
00:48:37,960 --> 00:48:40,820
[SPEAKER_01] u nekome, a pričamo centar desno,

1376
00:48:40,820 --> 00:48:44,059
[SPEAKER_01] o nekakoj novoj, ali novoj opciji

1377
00:48:44,059 --> 00:48:46,019
[SPEAKER_01] koja neće bljesnuti kao što smo mi bljesnuti

1378
00:48:46,019 --> 00:48:47,619
[SPEAKER_01] u DPU pa ćemo se lagano gasiti,

1379
00:48:47,619 --> 00:48:49,659
[SPEAKER_01] nego koje će stvarno imati nekakav kontinuit,

1380
00:48:49,659 --> 00:48:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] koje će na zdravim osnovama učiti

1381
00:48:51,340 --> 00:48:53,260
[SPEAKER_01] bez bilo kakvih skrivenih motiva,

1382
00:48:53,260 --> 00:48:55,300
[SPEAKER_01] bez bilo kakvih skrivenih priča,

1383
00:48:55,300 --> 00:48:56,980
[SPEAKER_01] da ih se može kupiti za ne znam,

1384
00:48:56,980 --> 00:48:58,159
[SPEAKER_01] za ovo i za ono.

1385
00:48:58,159 --> 00:49:00,119
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ćemo to dočekati? Ne znam.

1386
00:49:00,460 --> 00:49:03,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se nadam, za dobro biti Hrvatske čim prije.

1387
00:49:03,079 --> 00:49:06,579
[SPEAKER_01] Čim prije, jer ova kombinatorika

1388
00:49:06,579 --> 00:49:10,159
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo lako će se dogoditi,

1389
00:49:10,159 --> 00:49:12,400
[SPEAKER_01] nažalost, moram to nažalost,

1390
00:49:12,400 --> 00:49:14,739
[SPEAKER_01] da ćemo mi možda na sljedećem izborima imati

1391
00:49:14,739 --> 00:49:17,500
[SPEAKER_01] tu nekakvu ljevu koaliciju na vlasti.

1392
00:49:17,679 --> 00:49:19,619
[SPEAKER_01] A to će biti tek pogubno.

1393
00:49:19,619 --> 00:49:21,960
[SPEAKER_01] Jer, oprostite, mi cijelo vrijeme,

1394
00:49:21,960 --> 00:49:22,760
[SPEAKER_01] o danas sam pričao,

1395
00:49:22,760 --> 00:49:24,360
[SPEAKER_01] danas sam bio u kutini na jednom sastanku

1396
00:49:24,360 --> 00:49:25,559
[SPEAKER_01] gdje sam sa vrlo važnim ljudima,

1397
00:49:25,559 --> 00:49:26,579
[SPEAKER_01] uglednim ljudima pričao,

1398
00:49:26,579 --> 00:49:29,079
[SPEAKER_01] i mi smo pokušali rekonstruirati,

1399
00:49:29,079 --> 00:49:30,980
[SPEAKER_01] pa do 2000 teorijih vericiju,

1400
00:49:30,980 --> 00:49:31,719
[SPEAKER_01] ili sve naše izbore.

1401
00:49:31,719 --> 00:49:34,400
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo cijelo vrijeme imali situaciju

1402
00:49:34,400 --> 00:49:36,219
[SPEAKER_01] da mi glasamo za manje zlo.

1403
00:49:36,219 --> 00:49:37,880
[SPEAKER_01] Odnosno, mi glasamo protiv.

1404
00:49:37,880 --> 00:49:39,579
[SPEAKER_01] Mi ne glasamo za,

1405
00:49:39,579 --> 00:49:41,679
[SPEAKER_01] nego glasamo protiv.

1406
00:49:41,679 --> 00:49:43,519
[SPEAKER_01] I onda imate uvijek te nekakve situacije

1407
00:49:43,519 --> 00:49:45,019
[SPEAKER_01] da mi biramo od dva zla,

1408
00:49:45,519 --> 00:49:46,480
[SPEAKER_01] idemo birati manje zlo.

1409
00:49:46,480 --> 00:49:48,800
[SPEAKER_01] Bar iz ove perspektive ljudi

1410
00:49:48,800 --> 00:49:49,780
[SPEAKER_01] s kojima se ja družim

1411
00:49:49,780 --> 00:49:51,420
[SPEAKER_01] i nekakvih svjetonazora

1412
00:49:51,420 --> 00:49:52,300
[SPEAKER_01] kojih sam i sam,

1413
00:49:52,300 --> 00:49:54,360
[SPEAKER_01] ja nisam do sada imao

1414
00:49:54,360 --> 00:49:56,380
[SPEAKER_01] za koga rasovati.

1415
00:49:56,380 --> 00:49:57,599
[SPEAKER_01] Neko ko bi zadovolio

1416
00:49:57,599 --> 00:49:58,619
[SPEAKER_01] sve ove moje priče.

1417
00:49:58,619 --> 00:49:59,519
[SPEAKER_01] O sovrenizam,

1418
00:49:59,519 --> 00:50:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] nismo ga ovdje večer raz otaknuli.

1419
00:50:00,699 --> 00:50:03,400
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, apsolutna kategorija

1420
00:50:03,400 --> 00:50:04,780
[SPEAKER_01] koja je uništena u Hrvatskoj.

1421
00:50:04,780 --> 00:50:06,199
[SPEAKER_01] Sve ono što smo mi

1422
00:50:06,199 --> 00:50:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] krvlju natopljenu izgradili u državu,

1423
00:50:08,619 --> 00:50:11,019
[SPEAKER_01] gdje su puno naših branitelja

1424
00:50:11,019 --> 00:50:12,420
[SPEAKER_01] položilo svoje živote,

1425
00:50:12,820 --> 00:50:14,500
[SPEAKER_01] mi to šaptom gubimo.

1426
00:50:14,500 --> 00:50:16,800
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, nestaje apsolutno sve.

1427
00:50:16,800 --> 00:50:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] To sam nedavno isto dao jednu izvijevu.

1428
00:50:18,539 --> 00:50:19,380
[SPEAKER_01] Samo sam postao jedno,

1429
00:50:19,380 --> 00:50:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] po meni zdravo, logično pitanje.

1430
00:50:21,039 --> 00:50:22,500
[SPEAKER_01] Europska unija je tvorevina

1431
00:50:22,500 --> 00:50:23,219
[SPEAKER_01] takva kakva je.

1432
00:50:23,219 --> 00:50:25,360
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu baš tu nekakvi temelji dobri,

1433
00:50:25,360 --> 00:50:26,559
[SPEAKER_01] ali mi možemo reći sa sigurnoštvo

1434
00:50:26,559 --> 00:50:27,679
[SPEAKER_01] ona će trajati narednih 100 godina.

1435
00:50:28,099 --> 00:50:29,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ja postavljam pitanje,

1436
00:50:29,179 --> 00:50:31,460
[SPEAKER_01] što će se dogoditi za 10-15 godina,

1437
00:50:31,460 --> 00:50:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] karikiram,

1438
00:50:32,000 --> 00:50:33,320
[SPEAKER_01] ako se ona raspadne?

1439
00:50:33,320 --> 00:50:34,659
[SPEAKER_01] Što Hrvatska ima?

1440
00:50:34,659 --> 00:50:36,460
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko Hrvatska novaca ima?

1441
00:50:36,460 --> 00:50:37,880
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo ušli sad u monitelj.

1442
00:50:37,880 --> 00:50:40,380
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko smo mi, bogata zemlja?

1443
00:50:40,380 --> 00:50:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] Što će pripasti u tom trenutku u Hrvatskoj?

1444
00:50:42,500 --> 00:50:44,340
[SPEAKER_01] Prodali smo sve,

1445
00:50:44,340 --> 00:50:45,460
[SPEAKER_01] nemamo apsolutno niču,

1446
00:50:45,460 --> 00:50:46,480
[SPEAKER_01] monetarni sustav,

1447
00:50:46,480 --> 00:50:47,159
[SPEAKER_01] bankarski sustav,

1448
00:50:47,159 --> 00:50:48,639
[SPEAKER_01] to mislim da ne trebalo mi pričati.

1449
00:50:49,039 --> 00:50:50,599
[SPEAKER_01] Rasprodali smo sve što možemo rasprodali,

1450
00:50:50,599 --> 00:50:52,940
[SPEAKER_01] suverenizam u Hrvatskoj je nestao.

1451
00:50:52,940 --> 00:50:53,800
[SPEAKER_01] Izgubili smo,

1452
00:50:53,800 --> 00:50:55,119
[SPEAKER_01] znači naši branitelji,

1453
00:50:55,119 --> 00:50:56,920
[SPEAKER_01] dobili su sve bitke u ratu,

1454
00:50:56,920 --> 00:50:58,320
[SPEAKER_01] izgubili smo sve u miru.

1455
00:50:58,320 --> 00:50:59,420
[SPEAKER_01] Znači i to je,

1456
00:50:59,420 --> 00:51:00,920
[SPEAKER_01] kogod se ljutio na to,

1457
00:51:00,920 --> 00:51:02,559
[SPEAKER_01] a neka me bilo ko demantira,

1458
00:51:02,559 --> 00:51:03,320
[SPEAKER_01] neka me uvjeri,

1459
00:51:03,320 --> 00:51:04,099
[SPEAKER_01] ali argumentima,

1460
00:51:04,099 --> 00:51:05,579
[SPEAKER_01] ne floskulama političima,

1461
00:51:05,579 --> 00:51:07,800
[SPEAKER_01] neka me uvjeri da to nije tako.

1462
00:51:07,800 --> 00:51:08,320
[SPEAKER_01] To je tako.

1463
00:51:08,320 --> 00:51:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] Stvaranje, ovo što ste sami spomenuli,

1464
00:51:10,119 --> 00:51:11,760
[SPEAKER_00] stvaranje neke nove političke opcije,

1465
00:51:11,760 --> 00:51:13,840
[SPEAKER_00] i verujem da iziskoje zaista puno,

1466
00:51:13,840 --> 00:51:14,780
[SPEAKER_00] puno, puno vremena

1467
00:51:14,780 --> 00:51:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] i ne možemo nerealno očekivati.

1468
00:51:16,380 --> 00:51:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što je, recimo,

1469
00:51:16,960 --> 00:51:18,139
[SPEAKER_00] Dominski pokret napravio,

1470
00:51:18,139 --> 00:51:20,219
[SPEAKER_00] da je uspio u tako kratkom vremena

1471
00:51:20,219 --> 00:51:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] mobilizirati toliko ljudi,

1472
00:51:21,440 --> 00:51:23,480
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju su osvojili 16 mandata.

1473
00:51:23,480 --> 00:51:24,300
[SPEAKER_00] 16 mandata.

1474
00:51:24,300 --> 00:51:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] To je realno neki veliki broj,

1475
00:51:26,500 --> 00:51:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] ali evo vidite i sami

1476
00:51:27,480 --> 00:51:29,199
[SPEAKER_00] da se sad nalaze u nekim problemima,

1477
00:51:29,199 --> 00:51:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] kao što se sami spomenuli,

1478
00:51:30,539 --> 00:51:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, kad je Mirosloš Koro otišel,

1479
00:51:32,059 --> 00:51:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] kada ste vi otišli

1480
00:51:32,960 --> 00:51:35,260
[SPEAKER_00] i ostala ekipa koja je otišla od tamo.

1481
00:51:35,900 --> 00:51:37,139
[SPEAKER_00] Stvaranje nove opcije je nešto

1482
00:51:37,139 --> 00:51:38,219
[SPEAKER_00] što se zaista mora gladi

1483
00:51:38,219 --> 00:51:38,880
[SPEAKER_00] s nekom vizijom,

1484
00:51:38,880 --> 00:51:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] s nekim dugoročnim ciljem,

1485
00:51:40,139 --> 00:51:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] tako je.

1486
00:51:40,559 --> 00:51:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, recimo, što mislite o Mostu?

1487
00:51:42,960 --> 00:51:44,519
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su tu već nekih deset godina,

1488
00:51:44,519 --> 00:51:46,159
[SPEAKER_00] imaju te neke svoje ideje,

1489
00:51:46,159 --> 00:51:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] rekao bih da su dosta konkretni.

1490
00:51:49,039 --> 00:51:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] Zanima me vaša, vaša vizura je.

1491
00:51:50,539 --> 00:51:51,219
[SPEAKER_01] A, gledajte.

1492
00:51:51,219 --> 00:51:54,340
[SPEAKER_01] Sa Mosta sam dosta razgovarao

1493
00:51:54,340 --> 00:51:55,659
[SPEAKER_01] još dok sam bio u Dominskom pokretu,

1494
00:51:55,659 --> 00:51:56,519
[SPEAKER_01] tu smo mi pokušavali

1495
00:51:56,519 --> 00:51:58,039
[SPEAKER_01] nekakve zajedničke nastupe,

1496
00:51:58,039 --> 00:51:59,539
[SPEAKER_01] dogovoriti izlaske na izbore.

1497
00:51:59,539 --> 00:52:01,599
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, što misliti

1498
00:52:01,599 --> 00:52:03,480
[SPEAKER_01] u političkoj opciji koja,

1499
00:52:03,480 --> 00:52:05,340
[SPEAKER_01] sam mi ste rekli već deset godina,

1500
00:52:05,340 --> 00:52:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] je na političkoj sceni,

1501
00:52:06,480 --> 00:52:09,840
[SPEAKER_01] a ima 548 članova.

1502
00:52:09,840 --> 00:52:11,900
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je to malo,

1503
00:52:11,900 --> 00:52:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] znači, malo mi to smeta.

1504
00:52:15,039 --> 00:52:17,659
[SPEAKER_01] Koja politička opcija se boji

1505
00:52:17,659 --> 00:52:19,059
[SPEAKER_01] otvori prema svojim članovima?

1506
00:52:19,059 --> 00:52:20,940
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, pri tom ću vam samo dati komparacije,

1507
00:52:20,940 --> 00:52:22,880
[SPEAKER_01] radi, prilikom mog odlaska

1508
00:52:22,880 --> 00:52:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] iz Dominskog pokrata,

1509
00:52:23,539 --> 00:52:25,320
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo imali skoro 14.000 članova.

1510
00:52:25,320 --> 00:52:27,139
[SPEAKER_01] A bili smo mladi,

1511
00:52:27,139 --> 00:52:28,480
[SPEAKER_01] toliko koliko smo bili mladi.

1512
00:52:28,480 --> 00:52:30,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, i da se nije dogodilo to što se dogodilo,

1513
00:52:30,800 --> 00:52:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] danas bi Dominski pokret bio

1514
00:52:31,840 --> 00:52:35,260
[SPEAKER_01] debelo-debelo na jako dupla obite članova.

1515
00:52:35,260 --> 00:52:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, evo, sa 550 članova

1516
00:52:37,099 --> 00:52:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] imaju osam mandate u Saboru.

1517
00:52:38,980 --> 00:52:42,559
[SPEAKER_01] E, to je splet nekakvog okolnosti.

1518
00:52:42,559 --> 00:52:43,840
[SPEAKER_01] I ne kažem ja ništa,

1519
00:52:43,840 --> 00:52:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] znači, apsolutno su mi prihvatljive

1520
00:52:45,800 --> 00:52:46,800
[SPEAKER_01] neke politike Mosta.

1521
00:52:46,800 --> 00:52:49,599
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, opet se ni ja se ne mogu

1522
00:52:49,599 --> 00:52:50,440
[SPEAKER_01] otjeti o ome dojmu.

1523
00:52:50,440 --> 00:52:51,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam vam čovjek operativac,

1524
00:52:51,860 --> 00:52:53,679
[SPEAKER_01] ja vam volim povedzivati stvari,

1525
00:52:53,679 --> 00:52:54,639
[SPEAKER_01] ja volim graditi stvari,

1526
00:52:54,639 --> 00:52:57,840
[SPEAKER_01] ja volim stvari držati onako kako treba biti.

1527
00:52:57,840 --> 00:52:59,559
[SPEAKER_01] Što je planta svake političke opcije?

1528
00:52:59,619 --> 00:53:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] Da zastupa veći broj nekakvih ljudi,

1529
00:53:02,460 --> 00:53:04,460
[SPEAKER_01] pristaša, simpatizera, članova svega.

1530
00:53:04,460 --> 00:53:06,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ja ne dopuštam da se u moju stranku

1531
00:53:06,780 --> 00:53:07,719
[SPEAKER_01] učlanjuju ljudi,

1532
00:53:07,719 --> 00:53:09,400
[SPEAKER_01] a zašto ja to radim?

1533
00:53:09,400 --> 00:53:10,980
[SPEAKER_01] Bojim se za svoju poziciju,

1534
00:53:10,980 --> 00:53:12,340
[SPEAKER_01] jer svaki taj član nosi

1535
00:53:12,340 --> 00:53:14,099
[SPEAKER_01] na skupštine određene pozicije,

1536
00:53:14,099 --> 00:53:16,139
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda na skupština će brojati, ne znam,

1537
00:53:16,139 --> 00:53:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] 500 delegata,

1538
00:53:17,079 --> 00:53:18,659
[SPEAKER_01] pa će 500 delegata birat predsjednika

1539
00:53:18,659 --> 00:53:19,719
[SPEAKER_01] i cijelu tu priču.

1540
00:53:20,440 --> 00:53:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne volim takve stvari.

1541
00:53:22,000 --> 00:53:22,780
[SPEAKER_01] To me jako smeta,

1542
00:53:22,780 --> 00:53:23,900
[SPEAKER_01] to me jako smeta kod njih.

1543
00:53:23,900 --> 00:53:25,500
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, smeta mi kod njih

1544
00:53:25,500 --> 00:53:27,099
[SPEAKER_01] ovo,

1545
00:53:27,099 --> 00:53:29,599
[SPEAKER_01] znači oni su kao lepeza.

1546
00:53:29,599 --> 00:53:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] Znači neke,

1547
00:53:31,039 --> 00:53:33,579
[SPEAKER_01] u nekom trenutku imaju nekakve vrlo dobre,

1548
00:53:33,579 --> 00:53:35,039
[SPEAKER_01] važne, suverenističke,

1549
00:53:35,039 --> 00:53:37,099
[SPEAKER_01] a u nekom trenutku opet zastupaju

1550
00:53:37,099 --> 00:53:38,659
[SPEAKER_01] neke globalističke politike.

1551
00:53:38,659 --> 00:53:42,940
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da nemam baš nekako ni dobro,

1552
00:53:42,940 --> 00:53:44,780
[SPEAKER_01] a moram reći ni loše mišljenje.

1553
00:53:44,780 --> 00:53:48,139
[SPEAKER_01] Suradnja s njima je bila vrlo teška,

1554
00:53:48,139 --> 00:53:50,679
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo napeta u moje doba.

1555
00:53:50,679 --> 00:53:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, i oni apsolutno nisu bili susretljivi

1556
00:53:54,000 --> 00:53:54,340
[SPEAKER_01] i pregovorili.

1557
00:53:54,340 --> 00:53:55,840
[SPEAKER_01] Jer realno, mi da smo zajedno

1558
00:53:55,840 --> 00:53:56,860
[SPEAKER_01] u kombinaciji sa Mosvom

1559
00:53:56,860 --> 00:53:59,079
[SPEAKER_01] izašli na lokalne izbore,

1560
00:53:59,079 --> 00:53:59,860
[SPEAKER_01] mi bi pomeli.

1561
00:53:59,860 --> 00:54:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dosta se pomeli.

1562
00:54:00,699 --> 00:54:02,760
[SPEAKER_01] Zamislite, mi smo DP i tadašnje

1563
00:54:02,760 --> 00:54:04,500
[SPEAKER_01] osvoje 400 i nešto vječničke mandata.

1564
00:54:04,500 --> 00:54:05,639
[SPEAKER_01] I sad paljite,

1565
00:54:05,639 --> 00:54:08,059
[SPEAKER_01] oni kao deset godina stara stranka

1566
00:54:08,059 --> 00:54:10,480
[SPEAKER_01] osvojili su svega 177 ili 117,

1567
00:54:10,480 --> 00:54:11,219
[SPEAKER_01] nemajte me držav za riječ,

1568
00:54:11,219 --> 00:54:11,880
[SPEAKER_01] mandata.

1569
00:54:11,880 --> 00:54:12,980
[SPEAKER_01] A i to vam nešto govori.

1570
00:54:12,980 --> 00:54:15,119
[SPEAKER_01] To vam nešto govori o toj cijeloj priče.

1571
00:54:15,119 --> 00:54:16,559
[SPEAKER_01] A naša sinergijska snaga

1572
00:54:16,559 --> 00:54:19,179
[SPEAKER_01] u svim kalkulacijama davala je čuda.

1573
00:54:19,179 --> 00:54:20,179
[SPEAKER_01] Osvojili bi Županije,

1574
00:54:20,179 --> 00:54:20,960
[SPEAKER_01] osvojili bi gradove,

1575
00:54:20,960 --> 00:54:21,880
[SPEAKER_01] osvojili bi svašta nešto.

1576
00:54:21,880 --> 00:54:24,860
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to je poanta cijele priče.

1577
00:54:24,860 --> 00:54:27,579
[SPEAKER_01] Rušiti HDZ, pa ne rušiti ga

1578
00:54:27,579 --> 00:54:29,119
[SPEAKER_01] na parlamentarnim izborima.

1579
00:54:29,119 --> 00:54:30,440
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ako ga ne srušite dolje,

1580
00:54:30,440 --> 00:54:31,900
[SPEAKER_01] na lokalnim izborima,

1581
00:54:31,900 --> 00:54:34,039
[SPEAKER_01] ješto, o tu crpi ljude,

1582
00:54:34,159 --> 00:54:35,260
[SPEAKER_01] o tu crpi financije,

1583
00:54:35,260 --> 00:54:36,800
[SPEAKER_01] o tu crpi savuticaj.

1584
00:54:36,800 --> 00:54:38,619
[SPEAKER_01] Tek kad ga počnete rezati,

1585
00:54:38,619 --> 00:54:39,880
[SPEAKER_01] kolokvijalno rečeno dolje,

1586
00:54:39,880 --> 00:54:40,800
[SPEAKER_01] vi stvarate,

1587
00:54:40,800 --> 00:54:42,900
[SPEAKER_01] preduvjete da srušite HDZ

1588
00:54:42,900 --> 00:54:44,980
[SPEAKER_01] na nacionalnoj bazi.

1589
00:54:44,980 --> 00:54:46,699
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo to, recimo, pokazali,

1590
00:54:46,699 --> 00:54:47,760
[SPEAKER_01] mi nismo imali ništa,

1591
00:54:47,760 --> 00:54:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] osvojili smo 16 mandata,

1592
00:54:49,000 --> 00:54:49,440
[SPEAKER_01] i što sad?

1593
00:54:49,440 --> 00:54:50,519
[SPEAKER_01] A nemaš ništa,

1594
00:54:50,519 --> 00:54:51,599
[SPEAKER_01] u tom trenutku ti nemaš

1595
00:54:51,599 --> 00:54:53,079
[SPEAKER_01] nikakvu infrastrukturu na terenu,

1596
00:54:53,079 --> 00:54:54,099
[SPEAKER_01] nemaš baš ništa.

1597
00:54:54,579 --> 00:54:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam bio korinator

1598
00:54:55,420 --> 00:54:56,340
[SPEAKER_01] u devete izborne jedinice

1599
00:54:56,340 --> 00:54:56,980
[SPEAKER_01] u tim izborima,

1600
00:54:56,980 --> 00:54:58,800
[SPEAKER_01] a ideš ono ko siročić,

1601
00:54:58,800 --> 00:54:59,940
[SPEAKER_01] ideš od grada do grada,

1602
00:54:59,940 --> 00:55:00,920
[SPEAKER_01] nemaš tamo da nazoveš

1603
00:55:00,920 --> 00:55:01,920
[SPEAKER_01] hej Marko, hej Perov,

1604
00:55:01,920 --> 00:55:02,159
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1605
00:55:02,159 --> 00:55:03,159
[SPEAKER_01] evo mi dolazim dođe,

1606
00:55:03,159 --> 00:55:04,119
[SPEAKER_01] nemaš ništa.

1607
00:55:04,119 --> 00:55:06,119
[SPEAKER_01] I dobro smo mi napravili.

1608
00:55:06,119 --> 00:55:09,179
[SPEAKER_01] I da je tada DP ušao u vlast,

1609
00:55:09,179 --> 00:55:12,579
[SPEAKER_01] a on bi ušao da je ovaj zakon

1610
00:55:12,579 --> 00:55:14,280
[SPEAKER_01] i ovo je izbori kako treba,

1611
00:55:14,280 --> 00:55:16,840
[SPEAKER_01] da mi ne imamo osam manjinskih zastupnika,

1612
00:55:16,840 --> 00:55:18,280
[SPEAKER_01] da poštujemo i ovo je onaj

1613
00:55:18,280 --> 00:55:19,519
[SPEAKER_01] venecijansku komisiju

1614
00:55:19,519 --> 00:55:20,940
[SPEAKER_01] koja je rekla maksimalno četiri,

1615
00:55:21,039 --> 00:55:22,599
[SPEAKER_01] ali ničega se mi ne držimo onoga,

1616
00:55:22,599 --> 00:55:23,559
[SPEAKER_01] mi se držimo samo onoga

1617
00:55:23,559 --> 00:55:25,320
[SPEAKER_01] što ide njima u korist.

1618
00:55:25,320 --> 00:55:27,900
[SPEAKER_01] Samo da ne bi nekom krivo shvatiti,

1619
00:55:27,900 --> 00:55:28,679
[SPEAKER_01] nema apsolutno ništa,

1620
00:55:28,679 --> 00:55:29,980
[SPEAKER_01] nema problem nikakav

1621
00:55:29,980 --> 00:55:31,159
[SPEAKER_01] sa manjinskih zastupnicima,

1622
00:55:31,159 --> 00:55:31,579
[SPEAKER_01] da pa će,

1623
00:55:31,579 --> 00:55:32,860
[SPEAKER_01] da sam umogućen,

1624
00:55:32,860 --> 00:55:34,159
[SPEAKER_01] dao bi još osam,

1625
00:55:34,159 --> 00:55:34,659
[SPEAKER_01] evo 16.

1626
00:55:34,659 --> 00:55:35,079
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim,

1627
00:55:35,079 --> 00:55:36,420
[SPEAKER_01] uz jednu klauzolu

1628
00:55:36,420 --> 00:55:37,659
[SPEAKER_01] ne možete odrušivati

1629
00:55:37,659 --> 00:55:38,659
[SPEAKER_01] održavnom proračunu,

1630
00:55:38,659 --> 00:55:39,599
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1631
00:55:39,599 --> 00:55:41,360
[SPEAKER_01] samim time vi postajete

1632
00:55:41,360 --> 00:55:42,099
[SPEAKER_01] nevažan igrač

1633
00:55:42,099 --> 00:55:43,300
[SPEAKER_01] u smislu formiranja vlasti.

1634
00:55:43,300 --> 00:55:44,099
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1635
00:55:44,099 --> 00:55:44,840
[SPEAKER_01] aktualna vlast

1636
00:55:44,840 --> 00:55:46,480
[SPEAKER_01] nikad ne bi formirala vlast

1637
00:55:51,039 --> 00:55:52,840
[SPEAKER_01] nisu imali manjince,

1638
00:55:52,840 --> 00:55:53,699
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno veže tončiće

1639
00:55:53,699 --> 00:55:55,219
[SPEAKER_01] koji su još uz put pokupili.

1640
00:55:55,219 --> 00:55:57,679
[SPEAKER_01] I tada bi politička slika

1641
00:55:57,679 --> 00:55:58,619
[SPEAKER_01] u Hrvata bi bila

1642
00:55:58,619 --> 00:55:59,420
[SPEAKER_01] znatno drugačija.

1643
00:55:59,420 --> 00:56:00,880
[SPEAKER_01] I znatno drugačije bi se

1644
00:56:00,880 --> 00:56:01,599
[SPEAKER_01] išlo u jednom

1645
00:56:01,599 --> 00:56:02,639
[SPEAKER_01] sasvim drugom pravcu.

1646
00:56:02,639 --> 00:56:04,380
[SPEAKER_01] Mi nismo bježali,

1647
00:56:04,380 --> 00:56:05,739
[SPEAKER_01] tada nismo bježali od vlasti,

1648
00:56:05,739 --> 00:56:06,619
[SPEAKER_01] od govornosti vlasti,

1649
00:56:06,619 --> 00:56:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne u smislu da mi sad,

1650
00:56:08,079 --> 00:56:08,360
[SPEAKER_01] evo,

1651
00:56:08,360 --> 00:56:10,039
[SPEAKER_01] dočepali smo se mi sad vlasti,

1652
00:56:10,039 --> 00:56:10,340
[SPEAKER_01] to je to.

1653
00:56:10,340 --> 00:56:10,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ne,

1654
00:56:10,559 --> 00:56:11,760
[SPEAKER_01] nego jedan vrlo važan

1655
00:56:11,760 --> 00:56:12,599
[SPEAKER_01] i bitan korektiv

1656
00:56:12,599 --> 00:56:13,960
[SPEAKER_01] unutar te cijele vlasti.

1657
00:56:13,960 --> 00:56:14,679
[SPEAKER_01] Jer nekad,

1658
00:56:14,679 --> 00:56:14,920
[SPEAKER_01] znate,

1659
00:56:15,400 --> 00:56:16,219
[SPEAKER_01] to je u povijesti

1660
00:56:16,219 --> 00:56:17,380
[SPEAKER_01] moderne demokracije,

1661
00:56:17,380 --> 00:56:17,980
[SPEAKER_01] to je dokazano,

1662
00:56:17,980 --> 00:56:20,219
[SPEAKER_01] možete osvojiti sve,

1663
00:56:20,219 --> 00:56:21,780
[SPEAKER_01] a nekad da ni jedan presudan,

1664
00:56:21,780 --> 00:56:22,599
[SPEAKER_01] pa taj jedan može

1665
00:56:22,599 --> 00:56:24,139
[SPEAKER_01] kontrolirati tu cijelu prišu.

1666
00:56:24,139 --> 00:56:25,260
[SPEAKER_01] To su ti kontrolni mehanizmi

1667
00:56:25,260 --> 00:56:26,599
[SPEAKER_01] demokratskog sustava

1668
00:56:26,599 --> 00:56:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] koji su namjerno tako napravljeni.

1669
00:56:28,260 --> 00:56:29,280
[SPEAKER_01] Imaju oni svoji mana,

1670
00:56:29,280 --> 00:56:30,599
[SPEAKER_01] ali imaju i svoji prednosti.

1671
00:56:30,599 --> 00:56:31,360
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da...

1672
00:56:31,360 --> 00:56:32,340
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, prije mislije smo se

1673
00:56:32,340 --> 00:56:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] zatakvili teme

1674
00:56:33,400 --> 00:56:34,800
[SPEAKER_00] kulture dialoga,

1675
00:56:34,800 --> 00:56:35,860
[SPEAKER_00] recimo u našoj zemlji.

1676
00:56:35,860 --> 00:56:36,860
[SPEAKER_00] Dosta mi se nadoveza

1677
00:56:36,860 --> 00:56:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] na ovaj razgovor

1678
00:56:38,079 --> 00:56:39,320
[SPEAKER_00] što sad trenutno vodimo.

1679
00:56:39,320 --> 00:56:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko ćete vi

1680
00:56:41,019 --> 00:56:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] unutar udruge

1681
00:56:41,980 --> 00:56:43,780
[SPEAKER_00] provoditi neku kulturu dialoga

1682
00:56:43,780 --> 00:56:44,519
[SPEAKER_00] i mislite li,

1683
00:56:44,519 --> 00:56:45,300
[SPEAKER_00] evo, spominjali smo sad

1684
00:56:45,300 --> 00:56:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] nekoliko stranaka

1685
00:56:46,119 --> 00:56:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] od HDZ-a Mosta

1686
